values.content:
={{ $json.projectScope }}

Client: {{ $json.clientName }}
Industry: {{ $json.industry }}
Estimated Value: ${{ $json.estimatedValue }}

Generate a comprehensive consulting proposal including: executive summary, project objectives, methodology, deliverables, timeline, and pricing structure. Use professional tone and format.

parameters.jsonBody:
={{ {
  "emailSubject": "Please sign this document",
  "documents": [{
    "documentBase64": $binary.data.toString('base64'),
    "name": "Proposal.pdf",
    "fileExtension": "pdf",
    "documentId": "1"
  }],
  "recipients": {
    "signers": [{
      "email": $('Normalize Client Data').item.json.clientEmail,
      "name": $('Normalize Client Data').item.json.clientName,
      "recipientId": "1",
      "routingOrder": "1"
    }]
  },
  "status": "sent"
} }}

parameters.text:
=📄 New Proposal Created!

*Client:* {{ $json.clientName }}
*Value:* ${{ $json.estimatedValue }}
*Industry:* {{ $json.industry }}
*Date:* {{ $json.proposalDate }}

<https://docs.google.com/document/d/{{ $('Create Google Doc Proposal').item.json.documentId }}|View Proposal>

=🚨 HIGH-VALUE CLIENT ALERT! 🚨

*Client:* {{ $json.clientName }}
*Value:* ${{ $json.estimatedValue }}
*Industry:* {{ $json.industry }}

This is a priority opportunity requiring immediate attention!

<https://docs.google.com/document/d/{{ $('Create Google Doc Proposal').item.json.documentId }}|View Proposal>

parameters.message:
=High-value client proposal has been sent.

Client: {{ $json.clientName }}
Value: ${{ $json.estimatedValue }}
Industry: {{ $json.industry }}

Please schedule a follow-up call within 48 hours.

Proposal Link: https://docs.google.com/document/d/{{ $('Create Google Doc Proposal').item.json.documentId }}

parameters.text:
=⚠️ WORKFLOW ERROR ALERT

*Workflow:* Proposal Generation
*Error Node:* {{ $json.node?.name || "Unknown" }}
*Error Message:* {{ $json.error?.message || "Proposal creation failed" }}
